new graph "example/example2"

exec (::n)=init ;> (::n)=s(::n)* && rr

show node n

eval [?t\orderAscendingBy<numinc>\keepFirst(3)].map<int>{el:match<t> -> el.n.a}.sum()

show num nodes
show num nodes N
show num nodes M
show num nodes Root

exec TestSpanningTree ;> r((M)nodes(M).peek(0))

show num nodes
show num nodes N
show num nodes M
show num nodes Root

exec (::n,::m)=matchNM

show node n
show node m

quit
